    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811190/extras/a12402fad606c7bf88affc55ba2223ef.poster.avif?t=1771855119\" width=800 height=273 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811190/extras/a12402fad606c7bf88affc55ba2223ef.webm?t=1771855119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>《地堡笔记》</strong> 这是一部心理剧，改编自电影导演金成灿的同名短篇小说，并被制作成视觉小说。故事始于一场瘟疫，病毒以前所未有的速度吞噬着人类。主角是少数为此威胁做好准备的人之一。他成功地将自己封闭在一个自给自足的避难所内。然而，**孤独既能带来救赎，也可能引向深渊。**毕竟，铁门后的每一丝响动都可能是感染者，而每一片阴影都可能藏着要除掉多余口粮的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811190/extras/8b7657baefdef655006a474fba510bf6.webp?t=1771855119\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811190/extras/8b7657baefdef655006a474fba510bf6.poster.avif?t=1771855119\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=120 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>黑白色调的阴郁故事，背景设定在后启示录时代的欧洲🖊</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811190/extras/052bf4f1696b9e8b76fd4307843b5ece.poster.avif?t=1771855119\" width=800 height=229 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811190/extras/052bf4f1696b9e8b76fd4307843b5ece.webm?t=1771855119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>原创专业剧场级音效设计，搭配黑暗氛围声音🖊</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>沉浸于人性的恐惧与偏执的深渊🖊</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811190/extras/1bc8cad2750c8a6c13672a02d661c28b.poster.avif?t=1771855119\" width=800 height=229 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811190/extras/1bc8cad2750c8a6c13672a02d661c28b.webm?t=1771855119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>多重结局，每个都留下诡异的余韵🖊</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811190/extras/21788ef1b338787398012df82d0ec9b9.poster.avif?t=1771855119\" width=800 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811190/extras/21788ef1b338787398012df82d0ec9b9.webm?t=1771855119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>情感丰富的剧情，充满秘密与谜团🖊</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811190/extras/f8ba673d2f7f4213ca69122a8d9a121f.poster.avif?t=1771855119\" width=1170 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811190/extras/f8ba673d2f7f4213ca69122a8d9a121f.webm?t=1771855119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811190/extras/f8ba673d2f7f4213ca6